# Gallery UI design

When editing **`src/`** renderer files, follow the UX/UI constitution and design-token package.

## Read first

- [docs/design/UX_UI_CONSTITUTION.md](../../docs/design/UX_UI_CONSTITUTION.md)
- [image-scoring-ui UX_UI_CONSTITUTION.md](https://github.com/synthet/image-scoring-ui/blob/main/docs/UX_UI_CONSTITUTION.md)
- Skill: `.cursor/skills/gallery-ui/SKILL.md`

## Rules

- **CSS Modules** for new/changed UI — not new inline theme colors
- Use `var(--color-*)` from `src/styles/tokens.css` — **no new hex literals**
- Run `npm run design:check` when touching styles or design-package imports
